"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚耐   點發現</blockquote><br />\n佢之前借我hdd backup野<br />\n今日要用hdd<br />\n見到佢冇del backup<br />\n就好奇入去睇野<br />\n而家好奇心害死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘慘豬</blockquote><br />\n廢ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問下佢</blockquote><br />\n而家訓唔著覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果有扑咁又點？</blockquote><br />\n接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n講多少少背景<br />\n上年年中同佢一齊<br />\n上年年頭佢去旅行<br />\n上年年中佢話兩三年冇拍拖<br />\n<br />\n如果有扑即係唔係男女朋友都扑得<br />\n咁嘅話我實分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7b31ce32b1d6ec21dab2774fa85bedbe949d60","tid":236501,"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T18:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>How about this,<br />\n我兄弟同條女一齊咗5年<br />\n條女生日嗰個月慶祝完都好地地<br />\n轉個頭月尾就話飛去台灣去旅行順便探fd (台仔網友)<br />\n我兄弟本身話陪佢去  <br />\n條女就話想試下一個人去旅行<br />\n<br />\n到最後7日入面大部份時間十問九唔應<br />\n夜晚就算返到&ldquo;酒店&rdquo; (我都唔知係咪真係酒店),<br />\nWhatsApp都冇多個<br />\n<br />\n然後返到黎HK唔夠一個月就話分手<br />\n<br />\n請問係咪好綠</blockquote><br />\n綠<br />\n<br />\n起碼佢去旅行係同我一齊之前嘅事<br />\n就算係都只係比佢呃撚左<br />\n唔洗戴帽"},{"pid":"29ea53bf02496d26020cd2dd5031b50ed76b8ec8","tid":236501,"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁撚耐   點發現</blockquote><br />\n佢之前借我hdd backup野<br />\n今日要用hdd<br />\n見到佢冇del backup<br />\n就好奇入去睇野<br />\n而家好奇心害死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘慘豬</blockquote><br />\n廢ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/no